SBAR COMMAND

Syntax: sbar [on|off]

Toggle the status bar shown after each room move.

  sbar       toggle on/off
  sbar on    enable the status bar
  sbar off   disable the status bar

The bar shows HP, SDC, MDC, PPE, and ISP as applicable.
Use 'colorize' for a green bar.

See also: score, status, colorize
